# Open-source projects for LLM web search integration

**Over 150 open-source projects** now enable LLM systems to search the web, ranging from full orchestration frameworks to specialized reranking libraries. This comprehensive catalog covers every major category: orchestration frameworks like LangChain and CrewAI, self-hosted AI search engines like Perplexica, supporting tools like Firecrawl and Crawl4AI, and search API clients for Tavily, Exa, and dozens more. The ecosystem has matured significantly, with production-ready options available for every component of an LLM search pipeline.

-----

